strings:
<voice_0x01000B11><se_high>Jessica: We took care of the sea monster,
so I got them to agree to wait for us.
<voice_0x01000B12><se_high>Jessica: I figured you'd like to rest and buy provisions before we set sail again.

<voice_0x01000B13><se_high>Jessica: I'll be waiting for you here.
Don't take too long, now!
We've got work to do!

<voice_0x01000B14><se_high>Jessica: Actually, before we go, <most_heroic>,
I have a favour to ask.

<voice_0x01000B15><se_high>Jessica: You're after Dhoulmagus just like I am, right?
We're fighting for the same reasons.
<voice_0x01000B16><se_high>Jessica: So I was thinking, why don't we do this together? I haven't been studying magic for long, but I still have a lot to offer. What do you say?

<voice_0x01000B17><se_high>Jessica: No, huh?
Yeah, I expected as much.
It's a big decision, after all.

<voice_0x01000B18><se_high>Jessica: But I'm sorry. Once I've made up my mind,
I just can't let something drop.

<voice_0x01000B19><se_high>Jessica: It's just how I am. So I'm not asking you,
I'm telling you, <most_heroic>.
I'm joining your party!

<voice_0x01000B1A><se_high>Jessica: I've got a great feeling about this.
Thanks, guys.
<voice_0x01000B1B><se_high>Jessica: Well, now that that's taken care of, let's go!
<voice_0x01000B1C><se_low>King Trode: Just where do you think you're going without me and my beautiful Princess!?

<voice_0x01000B1D><se_low>Quartermaster: All hands on deck!
Weigh anchor!
Prepare to set sail for Peregrin Quay!
